It seems that original bug is outdated and caused by outdated standard.jar in
jakarta-taglibs\cache\lib directory of the package. I think it must be either
updated or removed.
creator: tivv@gtech-ua.com
pierre.delisle@sun.com
text:
Per the following comment:

  It seems that original bug is outdated and caused by outdated standard.jar in
  jakarta-taglibs\cache\lib directory of the package. I think it must be either
  updated or removed.\

Redirected this bug to the cache taglib.

Since this is talking about a nightly that is over two years old, I'm marking 
it as a WONTFIX. Please re-open if this is a current issue.
